wordpressPost.title: Check out the Øya 2015 schedule
wordpressPost.content:
The schedule for this year’s Øya is here! Check out PROGRAM in the menu to see who is playing where and when. Start your planning of four wonderful and perhaps hectic days in Tøyenparken. There are still tickets left for Wednesday, Thursday and Friday.

It will take a couple more weeks until we are completely done with programming all the club shows, and getting them into the schedule. We are also waiting for the full program for Biblioteket, our intimate tent for music, literature and more.

photo Erik Moholdt

messages.newsletter.consentText:
Øyafestivalen sender ut nyhetsbrev cirka 3-4 ganger per måned via
    e-post. Make AS er databehandler for nyhetsbrevet. E-postadressen
    lagres i en egen database, deles ikke med andre og slettes når du
    sier opp abonnementet ved å melde deg av via lenken nederst i
    nyhetsbrevet. E-postadressen slettes også om vi får tilbakemelding
    om at den ikke er aktiv.
